                        <interp inst="t18470816-name-180" type="surname" value="WARE"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18470816-name-180" type="given" value="ROBERT"></interp>ROBERT WARE</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">City-policeman.</hi>) I was at Blackfriars pier, and took charge of the prisoner—I found no purse on him.</p>
